Developer Terms of Use
des:
TCA Brain Teasers lets you print different puzzles and their solutions to your Alexa-enabled printer.

To use this skill say “Alexa open TCA Brain Teasers” 

Followed by: 
-Print me today’s puzzles
-Print me Sunday’s answers 
-Print yesterday’s puzzle

PRINTER DISCOVERY
To print with Alexa, your printer must be connected to the same wireless network as your Alexa device. To get started, first you’ll need to connect your printer to Alexa. Simply say “Alexa, discover my printer”, or navigate to the Devices screen in the Alexa App, select “+”, select “Add Device”, and choose “Printer” as the device type. Learn more at https://www.amazon.com/alexaprint
